
  Name:  telldir
  
  #include <dirent.h>
  off_t telldir(DIR *dirp);
  
  The telldir() function returns the current location associated 
  with the directory stream dirp.On success, the telldir() function
  returns the current location in the directory stream.On error, -1 
  is returned, and errno is set appropri-ately.
  
  Related Functions:  closedir, opendir, readdir, rewinddir, scandir
